Update README.md

Hi,

I have some suggestions for better clarity for this section:

01. In the sentence "This tools makes some important assumptions about your workspace" the word "tools" should be "tool" It could be rephrased as "This tool makes some important assumptions about your workspace".

02. In the sentence "and replaces < adn > for <= and >= and vice-versa" there is a typo with "adn" It should be "and" It can be corrected to "and replaces < and > with <= and >=, and vice versa".

03. In the sentence "Contributions for mutators are especially welcomed" it's more common to use "welcome" instead of "welcomed" The sentence can be improved to "Contributions for mutators are especially welcome"

Thanks.
